{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 135231, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "忘了tag了，然后，戈氏已经流芳百世了，不是反话", "timestamp": 1594810748, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135236, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你是不是不太了解当时的情况，当时是保守派发动819政变，从某种程度上戈尔巴乔夫和叶利钦当时是一条船上的", "timestamp": 1594810772, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135240, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 抱歉忘记了#政治相关#", "timestamp": 1594810797, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135242, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当时戈尔巴乔夫被软禁在他私人别墅里吧我记得", "timestamp": 1594810800, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135246, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 啊给洞主的怎么变alice了", "timestamp": 1594810832, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135253, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我是觉得819能改变苏联，各种资料里说民意还是不支持解体的", "timestamp": 1594810906, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135266, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 民意的确是不支持苏联解体的，但是民意对苏共的观感已经很....所以我认为就算819成功了苏联也救不回来", "timestamp": 1594810977, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135268, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 戈尔巴乔夫是不是在中国以外都是流芳百世的？", "timestamp": 1594810993, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135274, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "戈是废了苏联然后还世界和平吧。确实对人类来说贡献很大了。", "timestamp": 1594811055, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135276, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那毕竟别的国家没那么多精苏", "timestamp": 1594811078, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135281, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 主要是戈尔巴乔夫有改革的心，却没有这个能力。经济改革改的一塌糊涂，被苏联民众唾弃", "timestamp": 1594811140, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135283, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 世界和平了吗", "timestamp": 1594811146, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135286, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 一超之后美国对外战争就没停过，和苏攻美守的时候没什么区别吧", "timestamp": 1594811161, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135290, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 支持苏联存在，但是不支持苏共继续维持过去的体制。戈尔巴乔夫试图按照这个思路来改革苏联，被保守派觉得在乱搞，弄了八一九，反而彻底葬送了保守派，堪比皇道派发动二二六最后送统制派上台", "timestamp": 1594811204, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135292, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 苏联的手术是戈氏做的，但是苏联的病早就有了，而且戈氏顺应了潮流，反而是叶利钦之流比较有争议。我们国家因为意识形态的关系比较容易把苏联解体归罪戈氏，其实苏联解体岂是戈氏能控制的。", "timestamp": 1594811227, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135297, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "（再说，苏联解体对我们国家真是大大的好事啊）", "timestamp": 1594811292, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135300, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 叶利钦只是一个投机者。这一点从他后来炮击白宫上表现的淋漓尽致。比戈尔巴乔夫更不如", "timestamp": 1594811318, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135303, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 苏美那时候出现核平这种概率比现在要高得多吧。", "timestamp": 1594811334, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135312, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对我们国家是不是好事我没太想明白。。中苏1989之后关系正常化，卖su27等武器也开始接触了。苏联解体之后没人给我们分担美国压力了，直到911才迎来机遇期", "timestamp": 1594811406, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135344, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 和平与发展是冷战之后的主旋律。", "timestamp": 1594811657, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 135347, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 23257, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你说的有道理，我是这么理解的，苏联如果还存在，那我们的改革会面临法统性问题，正因为苏联解体证明了苏联模式的失败，我们才可以放开步子抛弃苏联那套模式。当然还有地缘政治的解释，聊做讨论", "timestamp": 1594811737, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 23257, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "#23249\n戈尔巴乔夫要是当年给塔曼师和阿尔法下死命令逮捕叶利钦和清场，是不是如今也能流芳百世", "timestamp": 1594810694, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782593, "url": "", "vote": {}}}